reviewText: When you watch biography channel, you only see biographies for current stars. These are older biographies that my wife really enjoys. We look forward to watching them. The Amazon description was very clear and accurate. The Amazon customer reviews were helpful. It was well packaged and arrived on schedule.

Interesting look at the lives and careers of Humphrey Bogart, Shirley Temple, Paul Newman, Katharine Hepburn James Dean, Clint Eastwood, Robert Redford, and even Betty Boop.  Narrative can be repetitious at times but we still found them worthwhile.

All I have to say is that this is a wonderful Box Set. If you love classics and want to know more about the ledgends of the silver screen then this is for you. Price is nice too, it's like you are paying for one and getting all the rest for free.
